        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>National Ocean and Coastal Security Improvements Act of 2021</b></p> <p>This bill funds through FY2030 and expands the National Ocean and Coastal Security Fund. The fund must be used by the National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration and the National Fish and Wildlife Foundation to award grants for protecting, conserving, restoring, and using ocean, coastal, or Great Lakes resources, including coastal infrastructure.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
